00:53:31,570 --> 00:53:34,870
Scott: There's a board that shows you which cards have been played with little gems.

824
00:53:35,570 --> 00:53:37,370
Scott: So playing this game... You don't have to count anything.

825
00:53:37,712 --> 00:53:38,174
Rym: Exactly.

826
00:53:38,214 --> 00:53:49,530
Rym: So playing this game lets you, as a player, who may not necessarily count cards in Hearts or Wizard or something else, feel what it's like to play a trick-taking game if you were counting cards.

827
00:53:50,970 --> 00:53:52,644
Scott: That is the magic of this game, and I just realized it.

828
00:53:53,370 --> 00:54:01,570
